{"type": "article", "id": 30537, "title": "用塑料编织袋制成的椅子", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-03T23:04:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160803174823ZVnuEoQsf40YewDJ.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>第一眼看到开罗 <a href=\"http://reformstudio.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reform Studio</a> 推出的这些椅子时，你或许很难察觉它们采用的并不是普通的织物坐垫。工作室特别开发了一种名为 Plastex 的环保材料，展现出了废品利用背后无限的可能：回收的塑料袋被工匠手工拆解成线状，再通过埃及传统的手织机进行编织。由于收集到的塑料袋颜色不一，每一件成品都拥有着独一无二的多色花纹。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803200523GophnXH3PYqty17M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803200524zjFOLpM3XhcESifP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803200525ofkyuR3gB5ZJC6iF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803200524OfX3ZPz6Q7l9mvUV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}